OL,6,FDuring this four-week transition
OL,7,Fperiod, it's been suggested there will
OL,8,Fbe no facility for covering breaking UK
OL,9,Fnews for a domestic audience.
OL,11,FMuch of the BBC News Channel's schedule
OL,12,Fhas been shared with BBC World News for
OL,13,Fsome time now. In early January, the
OL,14,Fpopular late-evening newspaper review
OL,15,Fprogrammes ` broadcast in the UK only `
OL,16,Fwere dropped.
OL,18,FSince January, UK-focussed live news
OL,19,Fprogramming has been restricted to
OL,20,Fweekday daytime slots.
