OL,6,F(_) Plans for Studio E beyond April are
OL,7,Funclear. Although the forum poster
OL,8,Fsuggests this studio might be
OL,9,Fmothballed, other sources suggest it
OL,10,Fwill undergo a technical refit and be
OL,11,Freintroduced on air at a later date,
OL,12,Fwith a new look. The studio has been in
OL,13,Fuse almost daily since March 2013.
